---
import CTAButton from "../ui/CTAButton.astro";
import NavigationHint from "../ui/NavigationHint.astro";
---

<!-- About Section -->
<section
  id="about"
  class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">About Tam Philosophical Counseling</h2>
    <div class="prose prose-lg sm:prose-xl prose-invert max-w-none mb-12">
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-6">
        You arrive with standing, not as someone who needs fixing. We recognize
        you as a growing and a knowing being — someone already able to engage in good
        philosophic conversation, whether you call it that or not.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
        Your philosophical counselor is an ally — a power
        listener who takes your mind seriously. Not someone standing, wisely, above you. You have
        reserves that we don't have; we have reserves you don't have. Both sides bring
        something, and the ongoing conversation is mutual and richer for it.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-400">
        Our counselors are certified by
        <a
          href="https://appa.edu/about/"
          class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 underline">APPA</a
        >
        (the American Philosophical Practitioners Association). With a background in
        software development, we've built infrastructure that turns
        conversations into artifacts worth keeping — audio files that join your
        library and clean transcripts optimized for AI collaboration.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Let's talk CTA -->
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <CTAButton variant="secondary" />
    </div>

    <NavigationHint href="#process" text="What to expect" />
  </div>
</section>
